summary: This mods adds neighbors that you can see in the interiors of whiterun
descriptionHtml:
This mod lets you see other houses threw out all the openings and holes there are in whiterun.
In whiterun there are a lot of these , just breezhome for a example it has holes in the roof , you should see you neighbors house but you do not , my mod fixes this.
it adds immersion in the interior cell of whiterun so interior feel like they should sins you can see other buildings 
this mod does not have transparent windows , sorry.

SYNHW is compatible with nearly all mods sins it edits the void , not the interior of the cell and its been tested with all lighing mod , do not worry.
Have fun
author: C0331
